subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Zlatan Ibrahimovic, P.S.G.’s star forward, was sent off under debatable circumstances, but the Parisians twice rallied to earn a draw and advance to the Champions League quarterfinals on the away-goals rule.
